		<div class="bg-gradient-to-t from-green-400 to-blue-500 shadow-2xl m-8 p-8 h-3/5 w-1/6 rounded flex flex-col
															  item-center justify-center cursor-pointer">
			<h2 class="font-sans text-4xl mb-8 text-white">
